OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day, with prolonged evening
OL,7,Fsunshine. Staying dry with long clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight and turning chilly in
OL,9,Fsheltered spots. Winds mostly light
OL,10,Fbut becoming breezier along the coast
OL,11,Fand over hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FDry and fine, with long sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Warm or very warm inland but a
OL,15,Fbrisk breeze, especially around
OL,16,Fcoasts, giving a noticeably cooler
OL,17,Ffeel here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
